      "span_text": "The present study also demonstrated for the first time that the combination of empagliflozin and linagliptin reduced the collagen deposition (Sirius red staining areas) and the expression of α-SMA protein, a marker of activated myofibroblasts (hepatic stellate cells) [CITATION_1] , around the central veins, as well as decreasing the expression of type 1 and 3 collagen mRNA."
